author: Colleen McCain Nelson
title: Obama Says Iranian Missile Test Won’t Derail Nuclear Deal
text:
WASHINGTON—Iranian actions, such as a ballistic missile test conducted last weekend, won’t derail the nuclear agreement with Tehran, President Barack Obama said Friday.
Iran has violated the test ban repeatedly, and the absence of a nuclear deal wouldn’t spur improved behavior, the president said.
